675
00:33:24,170 --> 00:33:25,570
I am a cardiothoracic surgeon!

676
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:27,360
That's still a doctor.

677
00:33:27,450 --> 00:33:29,030
Besides, other than you,

678
00:33:29,860 --> 00:33:31,720
I don't trust other people.

679
00:33:32,260 --> 00:33:33,830
So it can only be you, Xia Chu.

680
00:33:36,020 --> 00:33:37,350
