718
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:56,870
Did you receive anything

719
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,580
from him recently?

720
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:02,220
No.

721
00:37:03,400 --> 00:37:04,500
No.

722
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:07,260
Kill them.

723
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,950
He's dead! I know nothing!

724
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:12,220
Stop it!

725
00:37:12,600 --> 00:37:13,750
Don't hurt my mum!

726
00:37:13,860 --> 00:37:17,120
I have got the stuff. I'll give it to you.

727
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,480
Is this all?

728
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:31,770
Yes.

729
00:37:53,630 --> 00:37:54,560
Sir,

730
00:37:54,620 --> 00:37:56,520
