746
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:20,780
The ID of Zhou Lan, which
we have been monitoring,

747
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:22,990
was found to have been logged in

748
00:39:23,080 --> 00:39:24,240
by someone else at Xiong's company.

749
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:24,830
After that,

750
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:27,070
he engaged with someone
with the ID, Buddha

751
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:28,710
on City of Desire.

752
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:29,670
They agreed to pick up the goods

753
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:30,790
