801
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:20,420
[the people and things that interest me.]

802
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:24,620
I would like to ask
you for a favour, Mi Gu.

803
00:42:26,990 --> 00:42:28,090
Go on.

804
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:51,090
The test results are out.

805
00:42:51,240 --> 00:42:52,740
[How is it? Is it poisonous?]

806
00:42:53,400 --> 00:42:54,860
I can't exactly say it's poisonous,

807
00:42:55,120 --> 00:42:57,110
but it's not completely safe either.

808
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,300
What do you mean?

809
00:42:59,670 --> 00:43:01,500
Do you know about its characteristics?

810
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:04,100
[It dissolves very easily in water.]

811
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:06,230
That's right.

812
00:43:06,320 --> 00:43:08,350
The inside of the pill is porous,

813
00:43:08,520 --> 00:43:10,040
it dissolve easily in water,

814
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:11,590
making it easy for
the patient to swallow.

815
00:43:11,710 --> 00:43:13,730
This is the key feature
of 3D-printed drug.

816
00:43:14,590 --> 00:43:16,600
