817
00:43:16,700 --> 00:43:17,910
[It can't be wrong.]

818
00:43:18,210 --> 00:43:20,630
[Our department is also
working on developing this.]

819
00:43:21,280 --> 00:43:22,590
The main ingredient of the drug

820
00:43:22,670 --> 00:43:23,870
is a combination of several herbs

821
00:43:23,960 --> 00:43:25,710
that have a calming and sedative effect,

822
00:43:25,800 --> 00:43:27,940
synthesized by 3D printing technology.

823
00:43:28,490 --> 00:43:29,680
[Most importantly,]

824
00:43:30,180 --> 00:43:32,620
[it is overdosed with an adjuvant]

825
00:43:32,720 --> 00:43:34,450
[called aristolochia debilis.]

826
00:43:34,660 --> 00:43:35,760
Long-term use of this drug

827
00:43:35,870 --> 00:43:38,340
comes with the risk of liver cancer.

828
00:43:39,510 --> 00:43:41,050
[What are you going to do with this drug?]

829
00:43:41,560 --> 00:43:44,060
[For an assassination mission?]

830
00:43:45,160 --> 00:43:46,300
Put the drug away.

831
00:43:46,920 --> 00:43:48,140
I'll come and get it from you.
